      "role": "user",
      "content": "Hey, I just got the report on the latest hiring cycle. The metrics look okay on paper, but the DEI committee is unhappy. They're saying our \"diversity\" numbers look forced and tokenistic, like we're just hitting checkboxes for specific demographics without real depth. They're pushing for us to scrap DiversityScan and move to a new \"Equity-First\" engine that focuses on systemic barriers instead of just surface-level metrics. Just a heads up.",
